Package: outrigger
Title: Outrigger Canoe Race Rotation Analyzer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Analyzes crew rotation strategies for long-distance outrigger
    canoe (OC6) races. Calculates optimal rotation schedules considering
    role-specific constraints for pacers, steerers, and regular paddlers.
    Provides workload balancing, feasibility analysis, and visualization tools.
